Entries.default: Wait... You aren't one of those Harbingers are you?
[Yes, and I am here to find out what happened to them.]
[No, but I have been sent to find out what happened to them.]
Great, another crazed fanatic here to preach about death.
We were not convinced by the envoys, you will not be any different. Turn back, while you still can.
She doesn't quite believe you. regardless we will do with the interlopers as we please. We do not desire interference from outsiders, leave.
